===============================================================================

RailsI18nOnair has been installed!

Next steps:

1. Configure your storage mode in config/initializers/rails_i18n_onair.rb
   - :file mode - Uses existing YAML files (no database needed)
   - :database mode - Uses database storage (requires running migrations)

2. If using :database mode, run migrations:
   $ rails db:migrate

3. Start managing your translations!

===============================================================================
